8. Beverage:mirinda is in the middle
9. Nationality:spanish is on the far left
10. Cigar:old-henry is on the left or right of Pet:rabbit
11. Pet:ferrets is on the left or right of Cigar:siglo
12. Cigar:aquamarinemaster == Beverage:7up
13. Nationality:italian == Cigar:baccarat
14. Nationality:spanish is on the left or right of Color:aquamarine
15. Cigar:old-henry is on the left or right of Beverage:soy-milk

